%% Diagram: migration-recipe
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart LR
    A[1 Audit<br/>routes by content shape:<br/>per-user, change rate,<br/>build budget] --> B[2 Split rendering boundary<br/>SSG / ISR / PPR / SSR<br/>per route]
    B --> C[3 Cache strategy<br/>TTLs, surrogate keys,<br/>tag-based purge,<br/>edge bucketing key]
    C --> D[4 Strangler rollout<br/>10 to 25 to 50 to 100<br/>by route family]
    D --> E[5 Measure CWV<br/>RUM + synthetic + APM<br/>per bucket, per route]
    E -->|regression| C
    E -->|stable| F[6 Decommission SSG<br/>retire build pipeline]